;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Bottle neck finish (24mm, 28mm, etc.)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Product viscosity and density</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Dosage volume per press (0.5โ€“2ml)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Pump head material (PP, Aluminum, ABS)</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Formula compatibility</span></div>\n<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px;"><span style="color: #16a34a; font-weight: 900; flex-shrink: 0;">โ“</span><span style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">GMP certification and safety standards</span></div>\n</div>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Why Airless Pump Is Trending in 2025</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Skincare in 2025 is driven by Active Ingredients such as Retinol, Vitamin C, and Peptides โ€” all of which degrade when exposed to air and light. Airless Pump systems are the optimal solution:</p>\n\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Decorating Pump Dispensers for Brand Identity</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">Pump dispensers offer multiple decoration options to build a distinctive OEM brand:</p>\n\n<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0 0 2rem; padding: 0;">\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">โ–ธ</span>Electroplating (Silver/Gold) for Luxury brand positioning</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">โ–ธ</span>Matte or Glossy spray coating to match brand tone</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">โ–ธ</span>Hot Stamp logo on pump head</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">โ–ธ</span>Full bottle + pump set screen printing</li>\n 	<li style="padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 0; color: #374151; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; line-height: 1.75;"><span style="color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;">โ–ธ</span>Frosted/Transparent material for Clean Beauty aesthetics</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">FAQ โ€” OEM Pump Dispensers</h2>\n<div style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 2.25rem 0;"></div>\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 2.75rem 0 1rem; line-height: 1.4; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;">Conclusion</h2>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 1.25rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.85;">The right pump dispenser instantly elevates your OEM brand\'s perceived value. Especially Airless systems โ€” the preferred choice for next-generation skincare with active ingredients.</p>\n\n<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#0f172a 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">\n<p style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">Interested in OEM Pump Dispensers? Contact us for samples and a free quote.</p>\n<a style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.65rem 2.25rem; background: #F59E0B; color: #fff; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.03em;" href="/categories">Browse All Products</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'เธเธฒเธเธฑเนเธกเธเธงเธ” OEM เน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธญเธขเนเธฒเธเนเธฃเนเธซเนเธ•เธฃเธเธชเธดเธเธเนเธฒ Airless Pump vs Lotion Pump', 'OEM Pump Dispenser: Airless vs Lotion Pump vs Foam Pump โ€” Complete Guide', 'เธเธนเนเธกเธทเธญ