  (1871, 187, 'rich_text', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<!-- PASTE เนเธ Tab "Text" เธเธญเธ WordPress Classic Editor -->\n<div style="font-family: \'Sarabun\',sans-serif; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; color: #374151; line-height: 2;">\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: OEM เธเธทเธญเธญเธฐเนเธฃ โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">OEM เธเธทเธญเธญเธฐเนเธฃ</h2>\n<div style="background: #FFFBEB; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;">\n<strong>OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer)</strong> เธเธทเธญเธเธฒเธฃเธเนเธฒเธเนเธฃเธเธเธฒเธเธเธฅเธดเธ•เธชเธดเธเธเนเธฒเนเธซเนเธ เธฒเธขเนเธ•เนเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เนเธเธญเธเธเธธเธ“เน€เธญเธ เนเธ”เธขเนเธกเนเธ•เนเธญเธเธฅเธเธ—เธธเธเธชเธฃเนเธฒเธเนเธฃเธเธเธฒเธเธซเธฃเธทเธญเธเธฑเธ’เธเธฒเธฃเธฐเธเธเธเธฒเธฃเธเธฅเธดเธ•เธ•เธฑเนเธเนเธ•เนเธ•เนเธ เธเนเธงเธขเธฅเธ”เธ•เนเธเธ—เธธเธเธเธฒเธฃเน€เธฃเธดเนเธกเธ•เนเธเธเธธเธฃเธเธดเธ เนเธฅเธฐเธ—เธณเนเธซเนเธชเธฒเธกเธฒเธฃเธ–เน€เธเธดเธ”เธ•เธฑเธงเธชเธดเธเธเนเธฒเนเธ”เนเธฃเธงเธ”เน€เธฃเนเธงเธเธถเนเธ\n</div>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: เธเธฑเนเธเธ•เธญเธเน€เธฃเธดเนเธกเธ•เนเธ โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">เธเธฑเนเธเธ•เธญเธเน€เธฃเธดเนเธกเธ•เนเธเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เนเน€เธเธฃเธทเนเธญเธเธชเธณเธญเธฒเธ</h2>\n\n<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0.75rem; margin: 0 -0.75rem 2rem;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐ฏ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">1. เธเธณเธซเธเธ”เธเธฅเธธเนเธกเน€เธเนเธฒเธซเธกเธฒเธข</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">เน€เธเนเธฒเนเธเธฅเธนเธเธเนเธฒเนเธฅเธฐเธงเธฒเธเธ•เธณเนเธซเธเนเธเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เนเนเธซเนเธเธฑเธ”เน€เธเธ</div>\n</td>\n\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐งช</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">2. เน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธชเธนเธ•เธฃเธเธฅเธดเธ•เธ เธฑเธ“เธ‘เน</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">เน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธชเธนเธ•เธฃเธกเธฒเธ•เธฃเธเธฒเธ เธซเธฃเธทเธญเธเธฑเธ’เธเธฒเธชเธนเธ•เธฃเน€เธเธเธฒเธฐเนเธซเนเนเธ•เธเธ•เนเธฒเธ</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐“ฆ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">3. เน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธเธฃเธฃเธเธธเธ เธฑเธ“เธ‘เน</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">เธเธฃเธฃเธเธธเธ เธฑเธ“เธ‘เนเธกเธตเธเธฅเธ•เนเธญเธเธฒเธฃเธ•เธฑเธ”เธชเธดเธเนเธเธเธทเนเธญเนเธฅเธฐเธ เธฒเธเธฅเธฑเธเธฉเธ“เนเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เน</div>\n</td>\n\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐จ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">4. เธญเธญเธเนเธเธเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เน</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">เนเธฅเนเธเน เธชเธต เนเธฅเธฐเธเธฅเธฒเธ เธเธงเธฃเธชเธญเธ”เธเธฅเนเธญเธเธเธฑเธเธ•เธฅเธฒเธ”เน€เธเนเธฒเธซเธกเธฒเธข</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: เธเธเธเธฃเธฐเธกเธฒเธ“ โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">เธเธเธเธฃเธฐเธกเธฒเธ“เธ—เธตเนเธ•เนเธญเธเน€เธ•เธฃเธตเธขเธก</h2>\n\n<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 0 2rem;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; width: 50%;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> MOQ เธเธฑเนเธเธ•เนเธณเธเธฒเธฃเธเธฅเธดเธ•</td>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; width: 50%;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> เธเนเธฒเธญเธญเธเนเธเธเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เนเนเธฅเธฐเธเธฃเธฃเธเธธเธ เธฑเธ“เธ‘เน</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> เธเนเธฒเธเธถเนเธเธ—เธฐเน€เธเธตเธขเธเนเธฅเธฐเน€เธญเธเธชเธฒเธฃเธ—เธตเนเน€เธเธตเนเธขเธงเธเนเธญเธ</td>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> เธเธเธเธฃเธฐเธกเธฒเธ“เธเธฒเธฃเธ•เธฅเธฒเธ”</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Summary โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">เธชเธฃเธธเธ</h2>\n<div style="background: #FFF7ED; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;">\n<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.9;">\nเธเธฒเธฃเน€เธฃเธดเนเธกเธ•เนเธเนเธเธฃเธเธ”เนเน€เธเธฃเธทเนเธญเธเธชเธณเธญเธฒเธเนเธเธ OEM เธเธฐเธเธฃเธฐเธชเธเธเธงเธฒเธกเธชเธณเน€เธฃเนเธเนเธ”เนเน€เธกเธทเนเธญเธกเธตเธเธฒเธฃเธงเธฒเธเนเธเธเธ—เธตเนเธ”เธต เน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธชเธนเธ•เธฃเนเธฅเธฐเธเธฃเธฃเธเธธเธ เธฑเธ“เธ‘เนเธ—เธตเนเน€เธซเธกเธฒเธฐเธชเธก เธเธฃเนเธญเธกเธ—เธฑเนเธเน€เธฅเธทเธญเธเธเธฒเธฃเนเธ—เน€เธเธญเธฃเนเธเธนเนเธเธฅเธดเธ•เธ—เธตเนเธกเธตเธกเธฒเธ•เธฃเธเธฒเธเนเธฅเธฐเธเธงเธฒเธกเธเนเธฒเน€เธเธทเนเธญเธ–เธทเธญ\n</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>', '<!-- PASTE เนเธ Tab "Text" เธเธญเธ WordPress Classic Editor -->\n<div style="font-family: \'Sarabun\',sans-serif; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; color: #374151; line-height: 2;">\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: What Is OEM โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">What Is OEM?</h2>\n<div style="background: #FFFBEB; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;">\n<strong>OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer)</strong> manufacturing allows you to produce products under your own brand without investing in factory infrastructure, machinery, or production systems. This approach reduces initial capital requirements and accelerates time-to-market.\n</div>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: Steps to Launch โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">Steps to Launch Your Brand</h2>\n\n<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0.75rem; margin: 0 -0.75rem 2rem;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐ฏ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">1. Define Your Target Market</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">Understand your audience and establish clear brand positioning.</div>\n</td>\n\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐งช</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">2. Choose Product Formula</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">Select a standard formula or develop a customized formulation.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐“ฆ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">3. Select Packaging</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">Packaging influences brand perception and purchasing decisions.</div>\n</td>\n\n<td style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;">\n<div style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">๐จ</div>\n<div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">4. Build Brand Identity</div>\n<div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">Design your logo, labels, and visual elements carefully.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Section: Budget Planning โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">Budget Planning</h2>\n\n<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 0 2rem;">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; width: 50%;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> Minimum Order Quantity (MOQ)</td>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem; width: 50%;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> Design costs</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> Regulatory registration</td>\n<td style="padding: 0.45rem 0 0.45rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; color: #374151; font-size: 0.9rem;"><span style="color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 0.5rem;">โ“</span> Marketing budget</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; margin: 2rem 0;" />\n\n<!-- โ”€โ”€ Conclusion โ”€โ”€ -->\n<h2 style="font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: bold; color: #111827; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; line-height: 1.4;">Conclusion</h2>\n<div style="background: #FFF7ED; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;">\n<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.9;">\nLaunching a cosmetic brand through OEM manufacturing becomes efficient an